data.text:
Starting Line Stories, Levels 6-8. This book contains story starters and writing prompts, and it is divided into two sections. There are 70 story starters in the first section and 30 writing prompts in the second section. There are 100 total writing exercises.

This book is a stand alone program and does not require any other materials.
